data.description: Come check out this fantastic Orlando-metrowest home!! Home is 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, 2 car garage, with laminate wood floors in living areas, great size masterbedroom with huge remodeled walk in closet and nice walk in shower, remodeld guest bathroom ,spacious kitchen with appliances, Granite Counters and breakfast nook, covered patio, large fenced backyard with beautiful gazebo, great for relaxing and entertaining, newer roof. Located in the heart of metrowest, 15 minutes to downtown orlando and universal studios, 5 minutes to 408, shopping, and restaurants in metrowest and dr. Philips.All measurements are approximate and not guaranteed.
